@startuml sequence_board
!theme plain
title Partner Board (Kanban)

actor User
participant "BoardPage" as BP
participant "PartnersController" as C
participant "Handler" as H
database "DB" as DB

User -> BP: open /partners/board
BP -> C: GET /api/partners
C -> H: ListPartnersQuery
H -> DB: SELECT Partner WHERE TeamId=...
H --> C: rows
C --> BP: 200
BP -> BP: group by stage, render columns

User -> BP: drag card Lead -> InFunnel
BP -> C: POST /api/partners/{id}/stage {InFunnel}
C -> H: ChangePartnerStageCommand
H -> DB: UPDATE; INSERT history
H --> C: ok
C --> BP: 200
BP --> User: card lands in column
@enduml
